    }

    // ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏¢‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ complete
    function moveToComplete(taskItem) {
